column5: Anybody going too the Tool show tonight ? I lucked out and got an extra tickect from a buddy at work on Sunday, as I was up north Musky fishing when they went on sale. Can not wait it's going to be great.  Rob
Tool Show?  All I have to do is sit and my desk and watch all the tools walk by, tons of knobs too!!!
I am absolutely without a doubt going to be at the show.........thirteenth time for me

I saw them last night in Kingston with Tweak Bird.  .............What a freaking wild show!  I even thought TB was awesome....a 2 piece band with a guy that sometimes comes out with a flute or sax. Unreal!!! The drummer plays a wicked solo during Tools show.  As a warning though....but you may know this having seen them...don't bring a camera. They will take it immediatley and not return it; no questions asked!  Cheers,  Paul
crapppp man I wanna go so bad..I didnt see any dates for Montreal tho
